column5: AMC Aladdin continues to get better and better no one expected anything from it Updated from Deadline Yesterday off Disneys 4day Aladdin estimate of 1127M ComScore called the holiday frame for all films at an estimated 230M 1 ahead of last years Memorial Day stretch of 2277M Now with Aladdin coming in roughly 4M higher the Memorial Day domestic box office weekend should be at 234M the 6th best of alltime and 3 ahead of last year
